            "text": "Automatically generating a natural language description of an image is a fundamental problem in artificial intelligence . <S>",
            "relation": "BACKGROUND"
        },
        {
            "id": 2,
            "parent": 1,
            "text": "This task involves both computer vision and natural language processing ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 3,
            "parent": 2,
            "text": "and is called `` image caption generation . '' <S> ",
            "relation": "JOINT"
        },
        {
            "id": 4,
            "parent": 3,
            "text": "Research on image caption generation has typically focused on taking in an image ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "parent": 4,
            "text": "and generating a caption in English ",
            "relation": "JOINT"
        },
        {
            "id": 6,
            "parent": 5,
            "text": "as existing image caption corpora are mostly in English . <S>",
            "relation": "CAUSE-RESULT-REASON"
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "parent": 6,
            "text": "The lack of corpora in languages other than English is an issue , especially for morphologically rich languages such as Japanese . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "parent": 7,
            "text": "There is thus a need for corpora sufficiently large for image captioning in other languages . <S>",
            "relation": "CAUSE-RESULT-REASON"
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
            "parent": 0,
            "text": "We have developed a Japanese version of the MS COCO caption dataset and a generative model ",
            "relation": "ROOT"
        },
        {
            "id": 10,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "based on a deep recurrent architecture ",
            "relation": "BACKGROUND"
        },
        {
            "id": 11,
            "parent": 10,
            "text": "that takes in an image ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "parent": 11,
            "text": "and uses this Japanese version of the dataset ",
            "relation": "JOINT"
        },
        {
            "id": 13,
            "parent": 12,
            "text": "to generate a caption in Japanese . <S>",
            "relation": "ENABLEMENT"
        },
        {
            "id": 14,
            "parent": 15,
            "text": "As the Japanese portion of the corpus is small , ",
            "relation": "CAUSE-RESULT-REASON"
        },
        {
            "id": 15,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "our model was designed ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 16,
            "parent": 15,
            "text": "to transfer the knowledge representation ",
            "relation": "ENABLEMENT"
        },
        {
            "id": 17,
